                  <p>Debating whether upgrading my smartphone is worth it. Have a Nexus 6 that I’m really happy with except
                    photos. Now I’m not too much into photography and it takes good photos but these new phones like the
                    Pixel 2 have these great portrait modes, and I want to make myself look better for online shots. Is that
                    alone a good enough reason to upgrade? Like is the difference magical or just hype (as in make someone
                    meh looking look great)?
                  </p>
                </div>
              </li>

              <li class="media post">
                <div class="mr-3 actions">
                  <i class="material-icons md-18 md-dark">arrow_upward</i>
