                </div>
                <div class="media-body">

                  <span class="deletePost">
                    <i class="material-icons md-18 md-dark delete" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#deletePostConfirmation">delete</i>
                  </span>
                  <a href="editpost">
                    <span class="editPost">
                      <i class="material-icons md-18 md-dark delete">edit</i>
                    </span>
                  </a>
                  <h5 class="mt-0 mb-1">Post Title</h5>
                  Cras sit amet nibh libero, in gravida nulla. Nulla vel metus scelerisque ante sollicitudin. Cras purus odio, vestibulum in
